companyName: iShares Currency Hedged MSCI United Kingdom
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the MSCI United Kingdom 100% Hedged to USD Index, which consists of stocks traded primarily on the London Stock Exchange with the currency risk inherent in the securities included in the underlying index hedged to the U.S. dollar on a monthly basis.
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities (including indirect investments through the underlying fund) and other instruments of the underlying index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of the underlying index.
